# 6) Standardized artifact schema

Artifacts are internal structural things attached to an entity.

For example:

* UI components
* DB tables
* Queue messages
* internal modules

## Generic artifact object

```json
{
  "id": "artifact:ui:dsa-pricing-ui:PricingDisplay",
  "kind": "component",
  "name": "PricingDisplay",
  "description": "Component for displaying the current price of DSA",
  "schema": {
    "props": {
      "type": "object",
